1. *Imali* smo puno posla da obavimo (We had a lot of work to do). 
2. Oni *imali* su puno novca (They had a lot of money). 
3. *Imali* su problema sa računarom (They had a problem with the computer). 
4. *Imao* je puno knjiga za čitanje (He had a lot of books to read). 
5. *Imao* je jedan automobil (He had one car). 
6. Oni su *imali* veliku porodicu (They had a big family). 
7. *Imali* smo priliku da se družimo (We had an opportunity to socialize). 
8. Oni *imali* su dosta prijatelja (They had a lot of friends).